      "svgData": "./dsp/assets/svgs/Button.svg"
    },
    {
      "title": "Colors",
      "html": "<div>\n  <button class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-m-sm\" color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    Purple</button\n  ><button\n    class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple-cyan drac-m-sm\"\n    color=\"purpleCyan\"\n    m=\"sm\"\n  >\n    Purple Cyan\n  </button>\n</div>\n",
      "react": "<div>\n  <Button color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    Purple\n  </Button>\n  <Button color=\"purpleCyan\" m=\"sm\">\n    Purple Cyan\n  </Button>\n</div>;\n",
      "docs": "Buttons can be customized to use any of the Dracula UI theme colors, including all solid, gradient, and animated colors.",
      "screenshot": "./dsp/assets/ButtonColors.png",
      "svgData": "./dsp/assets/svgs/ButtonColors.svg"
    },
    {
      "title": "Variants",
      "html": "<div class=\"drac-box\">\n  <button class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-m-sm\" color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    Normal</button\n  ><button\n    class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple-transparent drac-btn-ghost drac-text-purple drac-m-sm\"\n    variant=\"ghost\"\n    color=\"purple\"\n    m=\"sm\"\n  >\n    Ghost</button\n  ><button\n    class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-btn-outline drac-text-purple drac-m-sm\"\n    variant=\"outline\"\n    color=\"purple\"\n    m=\"sm\"\n  >\n    Outline\n  </button>\n</div>\n",
      "react": "<Box>\n  <Button color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    Normal\n  </Button>\n  <Button variant=\"ghost\" color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    Ghost\n  </Button>\n  <Button variant=\"outline\" color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    Outline\n  </Button>\n</Box>;\n",
      "docs": "Dracula UI ships with three distinct button variations that allow for different levels of hierarchy and usage.",
      "screenshot": "./dsp/assets/ButtonVariants.png",
      "svgData": "./dsp/assets/svgs/ButtonVariants.svg"
    },
    {
      "title": "Sizes",
      "html": "<div class=\"drac-box\">\n  <button\n    class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-btn-xs drac-m-sm\"\n    color=\"purple\"\n    m=\"sm\"\n  >\n    xsmall</button\n  ><button\n    class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-btn-sm drac-m-sm\"\n    color=\"purple\"\n    m=\"sm\"\n  >\n    xsmall</button\n  ><button class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-m-sm\" color=\"purple\" m=\"sm\">\n    medium</button\n  ><button\n    class=\"drac-btn drac-bg-purple drac-btn-lg drac-m-sm\"\n    color=\"purple\"\n    m=\"sm\"\n  >\n    large\n  </button>\n</div>\n",
      "react": "<Box>\n  <Button color=\"purple\" size=\"xsmall\" m=\"sm\">\n    xsmall\n  </Button>\n  <Button color=\"purple\" size=\"small\" m=\"sm\">\n    xsmall\n  </Button>\n  <Button color=\"purple\" size=\"medium\" m=\"sm\">\n    medium\n  </Button>\n  <Button color=\"purple\" size=\"large\" m=\"sm\">\n    large\n  </Button>\n</Box>;\n",
      "docs": "Button sizes range from xsmall to large using the Dracula UI size scale.",
      "screenshot": "./dsp/assets/ButtonSizes.png",
